OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1774461963
OL,3,CThree small boats severely damaged in
OL,4,Csuspected arson attack at historic cove
OL,6,FThree boats have been severely damaged
OL,7,Fin a suspected arson attack at an
OL,8,Fhistoric cove in Cornwall, police have
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FCrews from Devon and Somerset Fire and
OL,12,FRescue Service were called to a report
OL,13,Fof a fire near the toilets in Boat
OL,14,FCove, Penzance, shortly before 3:30am
OL,15,Fon Friday, 20 March.
OL,17,FDawlish Fire Station attended, and an
OL,18,Fadditional pump appliance was brought
OL,19,Fin from Teignmouth.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
