FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1774461963
OL,3,CThree small boats severely damaged in
OL,4,Csuspected arson attack at historic cove
OL,6,FDawlish Fire Station says the fire was
OL,7,F"quickly spreading" and on their way,
OL,8,Fcrews could see "a sizeable glow and
OL,9,Fflames" in the distance.
OL,11,FIt added: "Using the attack line,
OL,12,Fcrews worked quickly to prevent the
OL,13,Ffire from spreading further through
OL,14,Fthe boats.
OL,16,F"Once extinguished, crews checked the
OL,17,Farea for hotspots using a Thermal
OL,18,FImaging Camera.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
