OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1774461963
OL,3,CThree small boats severely damaged in
OL,4,Csuspected arson attack at historic cove
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, three boats were
OL,7,Fseverely damaged by fire, and an
OL,8,Fadditional boat was slightly damaged
OL,9,Fby heat."
OL,11,FThe fire service believes the blaze
OL,12,Fwas started deliberately.
OL,14,FDevon and Cornwall Police says
OL,15,Fofficers are making enquiries and urge
OL,16,Fanyone who saw what happened to get in
OL,17,Ftouch via 101, quoting reference
OL,18,F50260069776.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
